from collections import defaultdict

def check_poker_deck_completeness(s):
    deck = defaultdict(set)
    for n in range(1, len(s), 3):
        card = s[n:n + 3]
        suit = card[0]
        number = card[1:]
        if number in deck[suit]:
            return [-1, -1, -1, -1]
        deck[suit].add(number)
    return [13 - len(deck[suit]) for suit in 'PKHT']
